{
  "stem": "4753.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And end of November or so, we did go to Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we there till, I think, middle of February, so about two, two and a half months, roughly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from Braunschweig, we did go to another place where that was surprisingly [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] big, terrible, big building.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know what was that originally, a school or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the big [? saw ?] where they had the roll call inside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the only place that the roll call was inside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we did work in a factory, what was 500 feet or meter down on earth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But from the building, we had to go quite a distance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And from there, we had to go with an elevator down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from there, we did go 110 steps down in the salt mine and 110 steps coming up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And next to that building, I was talking about where we stayed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was a private house, also used by us-- I mean, by the SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we called that the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one of my friend, because ten girls-- two, five, you know, who were standing in, in roll call every morning and every evening by each other, one of the girl's feet and hands froze.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "At-- in Braunschweig, that was open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she hardly could stand up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In Braunschweig, she wanted to stay inside in the barracks to go back to Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I didn't allowed her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because I said, if you stay in, when I come back from work, you will be nowhere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I wrapped her arm around my arm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I was pulling her to work every single morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that was very painful, especially for her in that cold weather.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But we made it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
